\s Safari yangu huku ikiwa hatarini
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Safari yangu huku ikiwa hatarini, na ikipita katika giza na jaribu, najua kwa hakika: \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd  yu karibu, ninamfuata mahali po pote. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nikiwa pamoja na \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit  sina hofu. Anipa furaha na heri rohoni mahali pote. Ikiwa nitayashiriki mateso yake, nitamfuata \bdit*\bdit Mwokozi\bdit*\bdit  hata mwisho. \bdit*
